name: SSF10
title: Site-Specific Factor 10
subtitle: Mean Diameter Nucleoli (MLN)
notes:
**Note 1:**  Record the mean diameter of the 10 largest nucleoli (MLN) measured on a tissue sample. The absolute values depend on the staining and imaging methods used. Larger values are associated with shorter survival.

**Note 2:**  Record the value as expressed in tenths of micrometers.  Record the information based on quartiles for laboratory standards if this is the only expression of results.
